    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/event/the-traveller/"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The Traveller"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Dinuk Wijeratne and Kinan Azmeh each left their mark on the SSO and we need to bring these two friends together for an unforgettable concert. We’ve handed over the musical reins and these two superstars will take us on a journey."
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/temporary/b84d805c-f985-4b2d-9234-4cda77d695c2",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/Blog"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/event/the-traveller/"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/temporary/6a96af30-1ada-4ccc-b469-0cdddc4fa875",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/WPHeader"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/event/the-traveller/"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/temporary/f7045e17-9e38-41f5-821f-ba22e12fcc10",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/CreativeWork"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/event/the-traveller/"
      }
    ],
    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n7:30PM, Saturday, May 2, 2026\nTCU Place, Sid Buckwold Theatre\n\n\n35 – 22nd Street East\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0C8\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nSave Your Seats\n\n\n\nDinuk Wijeratneconductor\nKinan Azmehclarinet\n\n\nSyrian DancesKinan Azmeh\nClarinet ConcertoDinuk Wijeratne\nSuite for Improvisor and OrchestraKinan Azmeh\nPolyphonic LivelyDinuk Wijeratne\n\n\nWhat happens when we turn the concert over to two best friends? Magic. Astonishing, captivating magic.\nThe debuts of Dinuk Wijeratne and Kinan Azmeh left their mark on the SSO in the last few seasons – it meant we needed to bring these two friends together for a concert that will not be forgotten.\nA destination unknown, we’ve handed over the musical reins to these two superstars to take us on a journey.\nAdd this show to your subscription package and save!\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  },
