  },
  {
    "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/temporary/a8a15657-52f7-4927-aa45-3b3c0468a730",
    "@type": [
      "https://schema.org/CreativeWork"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://saskatoonsymphony.org/event/amy-and-adele/"
      }
    ],
    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n7:30PM, Saturday, October 24, 2026\nTCU Place, Sid Buckwold Theatre\n\n\n35 – 22nd Street East\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0C8\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nSubscribe and Save\n\n\n\nJanna Sailorconductor\nElyse Evangelistavocalist\n\n\nThe music of two powerhouse vocalists requires a powerhouse in their own right to bring it to life!\nSaskatoon’s own Elyse Evangelista takes centre stage after wowing our audiences as part of the YXE Divas team. In this brand new show Elyse shows off her unbelievable vocal range and power in hits from Amy Winehouse and Adele Adkins.\nWith Janna Sailor returning home to lead the SSO, the evening features hits like Skyfall, Rehab, Rumour Has It, Valerie, and so many more!\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  },
