    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n7:30PM, Friday, December 11, 2026\nKnox United Church\n\n\n838 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H4\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nSubscribe and Save\n\n\n\nKarl Hirzerconductor\nCasey Pedensoprano\nOli Gusellealto\nSpencer McKnighttenor\nNicholas Borgbass\nSSO ChorusDuff Warkentin & Kerry Agnew\n\n\nMessiahGeorge Frideric Handel\n\n\nPodium Partner Karl Hirzer returns to the intricate music of Handel for a third year in a row. If you had a chance to see the SSO and Chorus led by Hirzer in previous seasons, you know we’re in for a special treat. \nWe’re joined by soloists Casey Pedin, Oli Guselle, Spencer McKnight, and Nicholas Borg, and the SSO Chorus led by Kerry Agnew and Duff Warkentin.\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
